= SDL_GetSurfaceAlphaMod =
Use this function to get the additional alpha value used in blit operations.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetSurfaceAlphaMod(SDL_Surface* surface,
                           Uint8*       alpha)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''surface'''
|the surface to query
|-
|'''alpha'''
|a pointer filled in with the source alpha value
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success, or -1 if the surface is not valid; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

